highlights.description: Stephanie describing now as an incredible opportunity to enable change in policing. Describes Dane County Sheriff's response to the murder of George Floyd.
Lydia talks about the Defund Police Movement and disparities between the movement and how people interpret it.
Heidi shares her concerns on homelessness in Dane County
Stephanie talks about community differences in areas of Madison.
Amanda talks about her own experience being Hmong woman
